snippet.title: Beerdy - Bruce Lee Central
snippet.description:
Welcome to Bruce Lee Central. The biggest Bruce Lee channel on the planet! 
I'm Bernard "Beerdy" McAlister. Former IFC champion and professional mixed marial artist. 


𝙒𝙚 𝙖𝙩 𝘽𝙧𝙪𝙘𝙚 𝙇𝙚𝙚 𝘾𝙚𝙣𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙡 𝙖𝙧𝙚 𝙥𝙧𝙤𝙪𝙙 𝙩𝙤 𝙗𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙮𝙤𝙪 𝙞𝙣𝙨𝙞𝙜𝙝𝙩 𝙞𝙣𝙩𝙤 𝘽𝙧𝙪𝙘𝙚 𝙇𝙚𝙚'𝙨 𝙡𝙞𝙛𝙚, 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙡𝙪𝙨𝙞𝙫𝙡𝙮 𝙤𝙣 𝙔𝙤𝙪𝙩𝙪𝙗𝙚!
Bernard McAlister himself will regularly create insight-videos of Bruce lee and share new and never before seen footage of the master.  

All audio & video footage on this channel was aquired and is owned by Bruce Lee Central Holdings. att: Bernard Mcalister /Daniel Johnston.
All rights are reserved.

For licencing of audio/video contact CEE Media holdings. Daniel Johnston.
